properties.Name: CustomerSex
properties.Description:
The sex of the Customer.

The sex of an individual can change over a period of time and are represented with 'period start date/period end date' qualifications, which represented the best case for knowing this information. The sex of an individual may change as the result of an operation or as the result of more (medical) information becoming available.
